Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  在这里做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿遥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都怎么了  是谁死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:03:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没死哦  在这里不能说这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座敷童子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  居然趁人之危
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法  买入吧  把十亿定金付了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮  你来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从经纪人那里听说了情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君回去拿东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是心脏的问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像之前就不怎么好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君又不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心脏…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…痔疮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君…是这么说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心伯父的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手术已经定在年后了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  他还年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生也说一定能康复的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦的是藤井君哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是家属吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病人现在醒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是森川由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦不…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是变漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我这副狼狈样真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋儿子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家去取东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本是想说出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看来是没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的冬弥君就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮  经纪人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么让她走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道我会回来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微拖延下时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人都会注意到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看她挺忙的  和你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让她赶紧回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  由绮小姐…森川小姐不是来见你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来看望我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是顺便来看望的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  都倒下了还色眯眯的  你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道伯父是因为什么住院的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴一辈子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从演唱会回去后就发现在门前一直等着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不联系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要责备她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是被要求保密了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间被占据  自己一个人整晚都在通宵咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啊」什么啊  站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你这孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没地方去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公寓口被监视着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么缺勤  为什么没来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  演唱会的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没我也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也为那些同样的曲子要唱三遍的孩子们想想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你  我们受到了多大的损失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  笨蛋  …
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手  把招牌弄坏了就得不偿失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏掉重新粘补起来不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是闹别扭的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱团输了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们输了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:11:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  胜负什么的随他便了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  你也明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方理奈的天赋  森川由绮的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有能对抗她们的武器这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些FANS对制造出来的专业歌手已经厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今后是外行的时代了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说教又如何了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发挥错地方的话就让人困扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂一个神崎树
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有打算永远都去关注她们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙混过关的  最多只能是两首
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁还没有出现明显破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停推出新的歌手…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推歌手又不是免费的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道在樱团上已经花费了多少钱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个笨蛋不做点什么的话  我们就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  我们就去交涉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就能见到绪方社长了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛瑙小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放她回公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到她不敢再犯为止  关到仓库里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  要去海边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会感冒的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  我输了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说输给由绮？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是  在说那种事！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个无所谓了  已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  遇到了塞车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了  待会再说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有比那个更重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我还要重要的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战利品的收取
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的是接下来的方针
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从昨天演唱会的入场来看  由绮的未来也定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈也可以看作是有所提高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来年的绪方事务所就是理奈和由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平分秋色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长  今天的课程呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈  重要的事是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈也很忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也许再见不到哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的话我也可以传话给绪方先生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是要自己说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的事情已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是出乎意料  这幅画竟然可以让你看呆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为这个国家空气的关系吗  和伦敦完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是别具一格的了  要变成自己的东西的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是第一次认输呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是昨天一晚的事情吧  接下来才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调羹  调羹调羹  没有调羹…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勺子  勺子在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  妈妈到哪儿干什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好吃饭才会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还是重要的考试时期呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你这样的朋友真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井老师也是个好人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  要飞喽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿遥  阿遥！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么来了  不睡着怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发烧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了阿遥的粥  已经完全治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就出门了  今天不回来了  大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以稍微远足一下也没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是圣诞节嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下一首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松山玛瑙小姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  让你监视我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又作歌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  干得不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱唱看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥生小姐  如果可以的话  要去echoes喝杯茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙你好意  但是我接下来还有个地方要去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就算了  别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧  彼此都是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话要对藤井君说的话  我可以转达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  您是为什么而来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？  没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为什么事都没有  才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筱冢小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有您的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是筱冢  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗兰奇  有事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.43,0:21:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人  到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是请回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能叫…  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说  是你叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.01,0:24:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十五页
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.33,0:24:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到的东西  会破坏周围
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.15,0:24:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不在那里  所以也无从下手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.69,0:24:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White  Album
Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--IN--
